id: pm-dita
title: "Nightly windows-latest STILL red after pm-i84i: scriptModule test harness imports .mjs scripts via absolute file:// URL, shebang survives missing transform (SyntaxError)"
description: "Nightly windows-latest / Node 20 remained red after the pm-i84i fix (run 27864828585, 2026-06-20T07:52, on commit 88aa1cbf which already contained the pm-i84i remediation). pm-i84i only fixed the sourceModule.ts TypeScript-source-import path; the scriptModule.ts harness (28 script specs) was missed and fails with the same SyntaxError class."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 2
